<h1>The Solar System</h1>

<br>

<p>

The Solar System formed approximately 4.6 billion years ago. It consists of the Sun and all the objects that orbit it, including planets, moons, asteroids, and comets.

</p>

<br>

<p>

The four inner planets are Mercury, Venus, Earth, and Mars. The four outer planets are Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, and Neptune.

</p>

